  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ten Bells is an anomaly horror game set in a timeless English pub. This unsettling escape room game draws you into a world of surreal anomalies and a hidden story, where every detail matters and the ghostly past lingers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >On Ten Bells:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“<i><strong>For real; W game no lie.</strong></i>” - CaseOh</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<strong><i>I started the game half-hearted and taking the p***, but by the end, I was fully tensed up and immersed. Nice job, Ten Bells!</i></strong>\" - Yahtzee, SecondWind</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<i><strong>This Is THE BEST Anomaly Horror Game Ever Made.</strong></i>\" - The Outer Middle Show</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<strong>[Clapping on stream to 14m followers] <i>This is one of the best anomaly games that i've ever seen.\" - Windah Basudara</i></strong>  <i><strong> </strong></i> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<i><strong>The SCARIEST Anomaly Horror Game...</strong></i>\" - POiiSED  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"<strong>The BEST Anomaly HORROR Game EVER Made\"</strong>.</i> - SWOL</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<i><strong>I've played almost every single anomaly loop game out there, and I can safely say this one surpasses them all by an enormous amount.</strong></i>\" - Thorlar</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ten Bells is a Spot-the-Difference Anomaly Horror</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the eerie timeless pub</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't find any anomalies, progress onwards</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you spot an anomaly; go back the way you came</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evade traps and the inhabitants of the pub</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the mystery through collected items </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach and eventually escape the Ten Bells</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...if you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/c26b4e85c49b4aae0c692afd1ed1933e.poster.avif?t=1772030191\" width=614 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/c26b4e85c49b4aae0c692afd1ed1933e.webm?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/c26b4e85c49b4aae0c692afd1ed1933e.mp4?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 55<strong> Anomalies:</strong> Discover anomalies to progress and uncover the story. Anomalies can be subtle, surreal, scary or deadly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/547a6fa0d37a223314455caf10ab8def.poster.avif?t=1772030191\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/547a6fa0d37a223314455caf10ab8def.webm?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/547a6fa0d37a223314455caf10ab8def.mp4?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unfolding Narrative:</strong> Discover objects that contain story elements, helping you piece together the spooky tale of the pub’s ghostly inhabitants. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/f2bdc89d2d23bc9ef255ee764d23c522.poster.avif?t=1772030191\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/f2bdc89d2d23bc9ef255ee764d23c522.webm?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/f2bdc89d2d23bc9ef255ee764d23c522.mp4?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Time:</strong> Perfect for a captivating stream or a chilling solo session, with gameplay ranging from 20 minutes to an hour. Full game from 1 hour 20 minutes to 3 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/00285614178da97e9a5baa6aa53bae87.poster.avif?t=1772030191\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/00285614178da97e9a5baa6aa53bae87.webm?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044030/extras/00285614178da97e9a5baa6aa53bae87.mp4?t=1772030191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you escape the pub and uncover the dark secrets of Ten Bells? Scour the pub, find the anomalies, and experience the horror for yourself.</p>",
